- Coiled Gold-Leaf 
            = High Stamina, Loot Bonus (5%)
  - Available to Coil Subs
  - Cannot Upgrade
  - C for Stamina
  - D for other stats

- Brass     = Balanced Stats, Brass Tacks (Xp Bonus, 5, 10, 15, 20%)
  - D => C => B => A for all stats

- Steel     = High HP + High Def, Steel Body (5, 10, 15, 20% of def to attackers)
  - C => B => A => S for HP and DEF
  - E => D => C => B for other stats

- Silver    = High Speed + High Attack, Quick Silver (Double Swing?)
  - C => B => A => S for ATK Speed and ATK
  - E => D => C => B for other stats

- Gold      = High Stamina, Loot Bonus (5, 10, 15, 20%)
  - C => B => A => S for Stamina
  - D => C => B => A for other stats

- Obsidian  = No Stamina, Balanced Stats, Threat Level +1
  - D => C => B => A for all stats
  - No Stamina Mechanic when equiped
